        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The IsC is currently working to digitize approximately 70,000 acres in 11 counties. Aerial applicators will use this GIs information to greatly increase the efficiency of their spray applications as they target Gypsy Moth infestations in Michigan.",
